[section:acknow Acknowledgement]

Evidently, __boost_assign_v2__ owes much to __boost_assign_v1__ (see its 
[@http://www.boost.org/doc/libs/1_46_1/libs/assign/doc/index.html#history acknowledgment section]) but it is also influenced by 
[tpl_range Boost.Range]'s [tpl_range_join `join`] and [tpl_range_adaptor range adaptors].

