inspired the changes proposed in the __url_boost_assign_v2_mini_review__.
* Thorsten Ottosen and John Bytheway have shaped this new version of the library and its documentation, through their feedback as review managers
of the __url_boost_assign_v2_mini_review__ and the main review, respectively. 

